Ŵanthu ŵa ku Japan ŵakutemwa kugwira ntchito za mawoko pera kuluska ŵanthu ŵa ku vyaru vinyake.
Suti yikaŵa cakuvwara ca bizinesi, ndipo ŵantchito ŵakacemanga ŵanyawo na mazina ghawo panji maudindo ghawo.
Kujiyuyura pa nchito nkhwakuzirwa comene, ndipo kukupangiska kuti ŵanthu ŵacitenge vinthu pamoza m'malo mwa kulumba munthu waliyose payekha.
Fundo iyi yikung'anamura kuti ŵantchito ŵakwenera kupempha dankha ŵalara ŵawo mazaza pa chilichose icho ŵakukhumba kuchita, ndipo ŵakwenera kupulikira kwambura kuŵafumba.
